Reactive omni widget layout with smart quarter-block packing

Replace rigid 2-column omni grid with a dense auto-flow layout where
the currency widget dynamically spans multiple rows in the left column
while compact omni items (Morning, HP, etc.) stack vertically in the
right column as quarter-sized blocks.

- Currency widget row-spans to match the number of compact omni items
- Wide omni items (>30 chars) still span the full width below
- When no omni items exist, currency expands to full width
- When no currency exists, omni items pair up in the 2-column grid
- Uses grid-auto-flow: dense for gap-free packing
